\newlabel{tab:sahi}{{4.8}{34}{SAHI slice-size sweep and TTA on the C2A test set for the recommended CBAM~+~P2 model, reported as separate inference-time settings (per-image box matching at IoU~0.5; latency is the mean per-image time on the 4070 Ti SUPER). The baseline row is the same model at $640$~px without slicing or augmentation}{table.caption.41}{}}
